I'm thinking about a project where it seems the defaults change mid-plan. The plan should ideally be stable — if old file-style generates from issue scans, it should stick with the project default during generation and not change afterwards. I wonder how this interacts with the config when no plans columns are present. We should consider using an event snapshot to ensure things remain consistent. It’s a tricky detail, but maintaining consistency seems crucial!
